@@TJvXMLDatabase
<TITLEIMG TJvXMLDatabase>
#JVCLInfo
<GROUP JVCL.Internet.ConvertersAndParsers.XML,JVCL.DBAware>
<FLAG Component>
Summary
  A component to access the content of an XML file using SQL like syntax.
Description
  TJvXMLDatabase is a component to retrieve data from an XML file using SQL like syntax. Specify the
  SQL string by assigning to the Query property. This component also has limited support for update
  statements.
  Note * All columns in the WHERE clause must be part of the SELECT clause as well * WHERE conditions
  must be enclosed in parenthesizes (i.e WHERE (Col1=5) AND Col2='Noodles')
  * Update statements are limited to simple operations (i.e SET Col1 = Col1 + 1, Col2 = 'FooBar')

